reviewText: Ugh. Poorly done. Don't waste your time.

I was very disappointed in this product.  I was expecting the lush green of Switzerland, but the first segment was mostly dirty snow and rocks.  Honestly, I thought, why would anyone photograph this.  The next segment was a lake and it did have more beauty in it.  The music was lovely, but all in all, I was disappointed and am returning it.
Very relaxing to watch before bed. Just beautiful scenery and music! I live in the mountains and I never get tired of it.
I love looking at different scenes from around the world. This did not disappoint. I would recommend it to anyone interested in travel.
